{"id": 7506, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "HL", "paper": "3", "year": "2019", "session": "19M", "subtopic": "a-10-environmental-impact—heavy-metals", "title": "19M.3.HL.TZ1.7", "topic_id": "a", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"specification\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">EDTA chelates with Ni<sup>2+</sup> (aq).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">[Ni(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>6</sub>]<sup>2+</sup> (aq) + EDTA<sup>4−</sup> (aq) <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\" \\rightleftharpoons \" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mo stretchy=\"false\">⇌<!-- ⇌ --></mo>\n</math></span> [Ni(EDTA)]<sup>2−</sup> (aq) + 6H<sub>2</sub>O (l)</span></p>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">Explain how entropy affects this equilibrium.</span></p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[2]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">State the number of coordinate covalent bonds EDTA forms with Ni<sup>2+</sup>.</span></p>\n<div class=\"marks\">[1]</div>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">entropy increases «and the reaction proceeds to the right»   <strong>[✔]</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">more species / free molecules are formed<br/><em><strong>OR</strong></em><br/>more ways of distributing energy   <strong>[✔]</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\">six    <strong>[✔]</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p>There were several incorrect responses that products were more ordered than the reactants.</p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">a.</div>\n</div><div class=\"question\" style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<p>Proved very challenging with very few candidates knowing the number of coordinate covalent bonds EDTA forms with a nickel ion.</p>\n<div class=\"question_part_label\">b.</div>\n</div>"}